  "detailed_description": "A survival horror game where you solve many puzzles, lure enemies into deadly and bloody traps and try to escape running away from twisted monsters chasing you in the dark. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nInmate 39 is a harmless little creature trapped in a horrific world his mind has created. You must help him escape this traumatic reality by collecting clues and putting the pieces of his life together. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFrom time to time Inmate 39’s alter ego, a deadly creature, will come to his aid, destroying everything in his path. Playing as the helpless and small Inmate and switching to the big deadly ally will present a fun and interesting gameplay experience.",
  "about_the_game": "A survival horror game where you solve many puzzles, lure enemies into deadly and bloody traps and try to escape running away from twisted monsters chasing you in the dark. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nInmate 39 is a harmless little creature trapped in a horrific world his mind has created. You must help him escape this traumatic reality by collecting clues and putting the pieces of his life together. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFrom time to time Inmate 39’s alter ego, a deadly creature, will come to his aid, destroying everything in his path. Playing as the helpless and small Inmate and switching to the big deadly ally will present a fun and interesting gameplay experience.",
